Googles Video-to-Video AI toolVeo 3is rewriting the playbook for clothing brand content. In this video, Christian Brennan from Bear Branding breaks down how to prompt like a filmmaker and generate viral, cinematic 8-second videos that actually sell. From TikTok hooks to Instagram-ready storylines, you'll learn how to leverage Veo 3 and Gemini (plus a sneak peek at Google Flow) to create pro-level visuals without a camera crew.
